## State machine AbsenceLog

```
received → processing → approved       (pseudo in AutoApprovalRules, PUT Furious ok)
                     → skipped         (pseudo non in AutoApprovalRules)
                     → failed_permanent (5 tentativi falliti o errore non-retriable)
```

Stati terminali: `approved`, `skipped`, `failed_permanent`.
L'hook `beforeChange` imposta `processedAt` automaticamente alla transizione verso
uno stato terminale. Mai impostare `processedAt` manualmente.

```typescript
// Hook da registrare in AbsenceLog
hooks: {
  beforeChange: [setProcessedAtOnTerminalStatus],
}

// Implementazione hook in src/hooks/setProcessedAtOnTerminalStatus.ts
const TERMINAL_STATUSES = ['approved', 'skipped', 'failed_permanent']

export const setProcessedAtOnTerminalStatus: CollectionBeforeChangeHook = ({ data, originalDoc }) => {
  if (TERMINAL_STATUSES.includes(data.status) && !originalDoc?.processedAt) {
    data.processedAt = new Date().toISOString()
  }
  return data
}
```

